spanGrp.span: ‘Road, river, trees, store, market; the road goes to a differente place;
Ñala diglö kal (hm) pe deli watuã'-glö deli tuã'-glö
Ñala mãu kwãwã (m) ñala bötöũ komĩ
and this other one goes to Olan;
this other one leads to Ujarraz;
it gets to the bridge and then to Ujarraz.
Once here, there are many houses,
Ya í tsõ-ka jeska (hm) tsõ-ka jes/ tã'ĩ jũ tsõ tã'ĩ jũ tsõ tã'ĩ (_)
kolejio yabla yur-gẽ eskuela yabla yur-gẽ
